headline: KLA (KLAC) Beats Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates

headline: Rockwell Automation to Present at Citi's 2026 Global Industrial Tech and Mobility Conference
summary: MILWAUKEE, January 29, 2026--Rockwell Automation, Inc. (NYSE: ROK) Chairman and CEO, Blake Moret, and SVP, Software and Control, Matheus Bulho, will present at Citi's 2026 Global Industrial Tech and Mobility Conference on Tuesday, Feb. 17, 2026, in Miami Beach, Fla.
